comment: Law of identity (reflexivity of class equality). Theorem 6.4 of [Quine] p. 41. This is part of Frege's eighth axiom per Proposition 54 of [Frege1879] p. 50; see also ~ biid . An early mention of this law can be found in Aristotle, _Metaphysics_, Z.17, 1041a10-20. (Thanks to Stefan Allan and BJ for this information.) (Contributed by NM, 21-Jun-1993.) (Revised by BJ, 14-Oct-2017.)
